---
title: Tropical Salmon and Shrimp with Stone Fruit and Hot Pepper Salsa
description: Taste the tropics tonight! Zesty jerk marinade and a perky stone fruit salsa brighten up this salmon and shrimp feast! Sweet corn and cilantro rice make a wholesome bed for all this bold goodness.
